  "time_ut": 1661487173,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b88\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Arrest of those involved in sale of column in Yali",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna has requested that 3 women, one man and the owner of the hotel who employed them, who were involved in the sale of udupathi in Jaffna city areas including Nallur, be remanded until the 9th. The judge ordered.",
        "The judge allowed the infant to stay with the mother and the other 6 children will be handed over to the child protection officers.",
        "Around Nallur temple and Jaffna city, women and children with infants were engaged in selling utupathi.",
        "In Nallur area, some people behaved in a disruptive manner by selling blowpipes to the people coming to the temple.",
        "On the basis of investigations, it has been revealed that they are brought in groups from outside districts and are staying in a hostel in Jaffna's Five Junction area and are involved in the sale of tobacco.",
        "In that situation, on Wednesday night, the Jaffna police surrounded the hotel and conducted a search.",
        "It is noteworthy that the police took 3 women, 1 infant, 6 boys, 1 man and the hotel owner who employed them to the police station."
      ],
